        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Chalarodes obpyramidata A ascomata B colony composed of conidiophores C, H, O-Q conidiophores D-G, S, T conidia I-L, R upper parts of conidiophores with conidia M asci with ascospores N paraphyses. Images: PDD 119363 (A-L); PDD 119364 (M-T); on natural substrate (A-N); in PCA culture after 4 wk (O-T). Scale bars: 250 μm (A, B); 50 μm (C, H); 10 μm (D-G, M, N, R-T); 20 μm (I-L, O-Q)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554158" .

